&lt;li&gt;Lead development of high leverage projects and capabilities of the Engineering team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and provide team leadership to your assigned Engineering function. This includes providing support on tactical team items and providing guidance to grow individual team members within their own careers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, recruit and maintain a top talent team, managing 2+ direct reports&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with architects and business leaders to design and build robust services using storage layer, streaming and batch data&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership for the overall planning, execution, and release of complex technical projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the VP, Engineering and drive the technical vision and strategy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with product management and UX teams to ensure we are building the best possible products&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review code to ensure it is efficient, well-tested, scalable, documented and optimal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Setup monitoring and testing of your APIs and services to better understand real time health of your products&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent a concept, the business area, and the company both in internal and external meetings&lt;/li&gt;
