&lt;p&gt;The Principal Data Scientist is a senior individual contributor and technical leader on the Customer Analytics team. This role leads the development and delivery of customer-facing analytics and data science solutions, with a focus on scientific rigor, scalable implementation, and measurable business impact.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position partners closely with Customer Solutions, Data Engineering, and Customer Success to translate complex business challenges into production-grade analytics, machine learning, and AI capabilities that improve product outcomes and client value.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
