&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a technical lead with a deep understanding of modeling methods from underlying mathematics, to assumptions, tradeoffs, interpretability, and limitations to ensure results are robust and reliable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use independent judgment and discretion to frame ambiguous business and customer problems into well-defined data science problem statements, project plans, modeling approaches, and measurable success metrics&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement advanced statistical and machine learning models end-to-end, including data pipelines, feature engineering, model development, validation, deployment, and ongoing monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with analysts to build reporting dashboards and data products that convert model outputs into clear, actionable insights for internal stakeholders and external clients&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
